Sentencas: An ionic-conducting electrolyte mainly governs the solid oxide fuel cell performance.
Titulo: Tuning an ionic-electronic mixed conductor NdBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ for electrolyte functions of advanced fuel cells

Sentencas: In this work, a mixed conductor NdBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+delta was tuned as an electrolyte via compositing with a proton conductor BaZr0.3Ce0.6Y0.1O5+delta (BZCY), which realizes an ionic conductivity of 0.16 S cm(-1) at 550 degrees C along with fuel cell power density of 470 mW cm(-2).
Titulo: Tuning an ionic-electronic mixed conductor NdBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ for electrolyte functions of advanced fuel cells

Sentencas: The 10 wt.% proton conducting BZCY can not only effectively block the electronic conductivity of NBSCF, but also greatly improve its ionic conductivity and the corresponding device's power output.
Titulo: Tuning an ionic-electronic mixed conductor NdBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ for electrolyte functions of advanced fuel cells

Sentencas: The interfacial conduction could take a crucial role in the ion transporting process of BZCY-NBSCF composite.
Titulo: Tuning an ionic-electronic mixed conductor NdBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ for electrolyte functions of advanced fuel cells

Sentencas: These interfaces or nanoscale grain boundaries formed amongst two phases keep excellent capability for designing and creating high performance electrochemical devices along with high-power density.
Titulo: Tuning an ionic-electronic mixed conductor NdBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ for electrolyte functions of advanced fuel cells
